{
  "text": "MWCNTs have also been covalently modified by functionalization with amino groups (-NH2), thiol groups (-SH), amino acids (-NH 3+ and -COOH), and Bismuth (Bi) which improved the selectivity and limit of detection. [CITATION_1] But then the covalent modification approaches require tedious chemical reaction procedures and thus increase fabrication complexity.",
